Notes
=====

I have tried to keep track of the reasoning behind various decisions I have made as I work on Blot. None of these decisions is fixed eternally, and I've changed my mind about various things. But it's easy to forget as time passes why something is so.

Whenever I have been mulling a decision about something difficult, I'm perfectly happy to accept a gut feeling as sufficient. If something doesn't feel right, I'm happy to hold off on it. Anyway, with that out of the way, here are my notes on the project: